OL,7,FAn "organisational failure" in police
OL,8,Fcall handling procedures meant a woman
OL,9,Fendured "almost incomprehensible"
OL,10,Fsuffering, after her crashed car, a
OL,11,Ffatal accident inquiry has found.
OL,13,FLamara Bell, a mother-of-two, and John
OL,14,FYuill, a father-of-five, died after
OL,15,Fthe car they were in left the M9 near
OL,16,FStirling on July 5 2015, as they drove
OL,17,Fback from a camping trip.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G1/13
