OL,7,FThey lay in their Renault Clio for
OL,8,Fthree days before being discovered on
OL,9,FJuly 8, despite police having being
OL,10,Falerted to the incident
OL,12,FMr Yuill, aged 28, was pronounced dead
OL,13,Fat the scene. Ms Bell, aged 25, died
OL,14,Ffour days later at hospital.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G2/13
