OL,7,FThe inquiry heard that, while Mr Yuill
OL,8,Fsuffered unsurvivable injuries in the
OL,9,Fcrash, Ms Bell would probably have
OL,10,Fsurvived if she had received medical
OL,11,Fattention on July 5 - albeit with
OL,12,Fpotential long-term neurological
OL,13,Fdeficits.
OL,15,FThe failure of Police Scotland to
OL,16,Fproperly log a call made to report the
OL,17,Fcrash had "fatal consequences for
OL,18,FLamara Bell," according to Sheriff
OL,19,FJames Williamson. ", terribly injured
OL,20,Fby conscious, is almost
OL,21,Fincomprehensible," he said.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G3/13
