OL,7,F'Confused, fractious working
OL,8,Fenvironment'
OL,10,FIn his determination published
OL,11,Ffollowing the fatal accident inquiry,
OL,12,FSheriff Williamson said there was no
OL,13,Fsystem of reconciling information
OL,14,Frecorded by officers in notebooks with
OL,15,Faction taken.
