OL,7,F"The failure of Police Scotland to
OL,8,Fproperly risk assess the call handling
OL,9,Fprocedures and have a system of
OL,10,Freconciliation was an organisational
OL,11,Ffailure" which "led to the safety of
OL,12,Fthe public being compromised and to
OL,13,Fthe events of July 5, 2015," he said.
OL,15,FThe inquiry also found a police
OL,16,Fofficer who failed to log a call
OL,17,Freporting the incident was
OL,18,Finadequately trained.
