OL,7,FSheriff Williamson noted the Bilston
OL,8,FGlen police was under pressure that
OL,9,Fsummer amid staffing shortages.
OL,11,FPolice sergeant Brian Henry, now
OL,12,Fretired, volunteered to do overtime at
OL,13,FBilston Glen, arriving into what the
OL,14,Fsheriff described as a "confused,
OL,15,Ffractious working environment."
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G6/13
