OL,7,FOn July 5, he took a call from farmer
OL,8,FJohn Wilson reporting a car off the
OL,9,Froad and recorded it in his police
OL,10,Fnotebook, but he failed to log it into
OL,11,Fthe case management system and no
OL,12,Ffurther action was taken.
OL,14,FThat meant that "Lamara Bell was left
OL,15,Fin a vehicle by the side of a major
OL,16,Fmotorway in Scotland suffering
OL,17,Fdevastating injuries," he said.
OL,19,F"These injuries, together with a delay
OL,20,Fin rescuing and treating her, led to
OL,21,Fher death."
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G7/13
