OL,7,FThe car was eventually discovered
OL,8,Fafter another member of the public
OL,9,Freported it to the police on July 8,
OL,10,Fand
OL,12,FBut Sheriff Williamson stressed that
OL,13,F"it would be wrong to interpret that
OL,14,Fas blaming Brian Henry," who he said
OL,15,Fhad been "inadequately trained and
OL,16,Fleft largely unsupervised to operate a
OL,17,Fsystem that allowed for human error to
OL,18,Fgo undetected."
