OL,7,FSince the incident in 2015, the police
OL,8,FContact, Command and Control Division
OL,9,Fhas been transformed into an
OL,10,F"efficient, tightly-controlled and
OL,11,Fsophisticated" network, Sheriff
OL,12,FWilliamson said, that is better able
OL,13,Fto serve and protect the public than
OL,14,Fin 2015.
OL,16,FHe said that while it is not "risk
OL,17,Ffree" and still "has a susceptibility
OL,18,Fto human failure", "the risk of that
OL,19,Ffailure going undetected is now
OL,20,Fmarginal."
