OL,7,FThe inquiry came after was awarded
OL,8,Fmore than #1 million in damages from
OL,9,FPolice Scotland in a civil settlement
OL,10,Fin December 2021. In September 2021,
OL,11,Fthe force apologised after being fined
OL,12,F#100,000 by the high court in
OL,13,FEdinburgh.
OL,15,FResponding to the inquiry, the force's
OL,16,FDeputy Chief Constable Alan Speirs
OL,17,Fsaid "Lamara Bell and John Yuill's
OL,18,Fdeaths were a tragedy and my first
OL,19,Fthoughts today are with their family
OL,20,Fand friends.
