OL,7,F"failed Lamara and John in 2015 and I
OL,8,Frepeat the personal apology made
OL,9,Fpreviously to their loved ones. We did
OL,10,Fnot keep them safe in their time of
OL,11,Fneed as was our duty and for that I am
OL,12,Ftruly sorry."
